{"segment":1,"line_start":1,"line_end":58,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_wu_fu","speaker_name":"伍孚","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"大人莫记小人过，小人有时虽是口不对心，只因身不由己，请左相、项大人和诸位达官贵人，原谅则个。","tone":"恳求","chapter":202,"line_start":10,"line_end":11},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_wu_fu","text":"伍楼主客气，今晚寡……哈！今晚秦某远道而来，正是要见识一下贵楼'醉风四花'的色艺，楼主给我好好安排吧！","tone":"豪迈","chapter":202,"line_start":28,"line_end":31},{"speaker":"char_wu_fu","speaker_name":"伍孚","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"这事有点困难，待小人安排一下，怎也设法让她们抽身来侍奉各位大人一会儿。","tone":"陈述","chapter":202,"line_start":42,"line_end":44},{"speaker":"char_jing_jun","speaker_name":"荆俊","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"'疤脸'国兴来了，还有常杰。哈！这群混蛋定是活得不耐烦，竟在睁眉怒目呢！","tone":"调侃","chapter":202,"line_start":46,"line_end":48},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":null,"text":"这些是什么人物？","tone":"疑问","chapter":202,"line_start":56,"line_end":57}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_xiang_shao_long","name":"项少龙","alias":[],"identity":"穿越者、秦国左相国","faction":"faction_guo_qin","role":"protagonist","archetype":"warrior","rank":"炉火纯青","one_line":"穿越至战国的现代人，秦国重臣，武艺高强","personality":{"traits":["机智","果敢","重情义","幽默","临危不乱","善于察言观色"],"speech_style":"轻松随和，偶尔调侃","temperament":"沉稳冷静"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_xiao_pan","type":"师徒","intensity":90,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"辅佐培育"},{"target":"char_jing_jun","type":"挚友","intensity":80,"bond_level":4,"dynamic":"兄弟情深"},{"target":"char_teng_yi","type":"挚友","intensity":85,"bond_level":5,"dynamic":"义结金兰"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[202],"source_refs":[{"chapter":202,"line_start":4,"line_end":5,"text":"项少龙和小盘研究过后，决定只带十八铁卫和另外十八名御前高手入内"}]},{"id":"char_xiao_pan","name":"小盘","alias":["秦始","秦公子","秦大官人"],"identity":"秦国太子、未来的秦始皇","faction":"faction_guo_qin","role":"protagonist","archetype":"scholar","rank":"初窥门径","one_line":"秦国太子嬴政，未来统一六国的秦始皇，少年老成","personality":{"traits":["少年老成","威严","有主见","偶尔小孩心性","果断","有帝王气度"],"speech_style":"自有一股威势，偶尔流露