{"segment":2,"line_start":59,"line_end":150,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_chang_ping_jun","speaker_name":"昌平君","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"是渭南武士行馆的教席国兴和常杰。","tone":"陈述","chapter":202,"line_start":60,"line_end":60},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"今晚是来作乐啊！","tone":"恳求","chapter":202,"line_start":64,"line_end":65},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"对！对！我们进去玩耍。","tone":"欣喜","chapter":202,"line_start":69,"line_end":70},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"把门人","listener":null,"text":"屯留蒲大爷到！","tone":"陈述","chapter":202,"line_start":74,"line_end":74},{"speaker":"char_guo_xing","speaker_name":"国兴","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"诸位大人请留步！","tone":"沉声","chapter":202,"line_start":96,"line_end":97},{"speaker":"char_guo_xing","speaker_name":"国兴","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"小人谨在此预祝项大人明晚旗开得胜、盛名不坠。","tone":"陈述","chapter":202,"line_start":106,"line_end":107},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_guo_xing","text":"国兄有何指教？","tone":"淡然","chapter":202,"line_start":110,"line_end":110},{"speaker":"char_guo_xing","speaker_name":"国兴","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"敝馆上下对项大人的剑术非常钦佩，若改天大人有空，请到敝馆一行，好让小人们有机会受大人指点。","tone":"陈述","chapter":202,"line_start":112,"line_end":113},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_guo_xing","text":"贵馆一向这么关心我项少龙，我早想登门拜访，这样吧！看看我的心情哪一天比较坏一点，就来找你们见识见识。","tone":"淡然","chapter":202,"line_start":122,"line_end":125},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"说得好！到时项大人勿漏了我。","tone":"豪迈","chapter":202,"line_start":129,"line_end":130},{"speaker":"char_guo_xing","speaker_name":"国兴","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"阁下何人？","tone":"厉声","chapter":202,"line_start":132,"line_end":133},{"speaker":"char_yu_wei","speaker_name":"御卫","listener":"char_guo_xing","text":"竟敢对……嘿！对公子无礼，给我跪下。","tone":"厉声","chapter":202,"line_start":140,"line_end":140},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_xiao_pan","text":"秦兄何须为这等人败了雅兴，我们还是寻乐去吧！","tone":"调侃","chapter":202,"line_start":146,"line_end":147}],"new_entities":{},"entity_updates":[{"id":"char_guo_xing","updates":{"source_refs":[{"chapter":202,"line_start":106,"line_end":108,"text":"小人谨在此预祝项大人明晚旗开得胜、盛名不坠"}]},"relationship_updates":[{"action":"update","target":"char_xiang_shao_long","type":"对手","intensity":65,"bond_level":2,"dynamic":"公然搦战"}]}]}
{"segment":3,"line_start":151,"line_end":268,"dialogues":[{"speaker":"char_jing_jun","speaker_name":"荆俊","listener":"char_yang_duan_he","text":"储君来了，但千万不要下跪见礼。","tone":"低语","chapter":202,"line_start":162,"line_end":162},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":null,"text":"各位兄台随便谈笑，像平时那样。","tone":"微笑","chapter":202,"line_start":174,"line_end":174},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_yang_duan_he","text":"杨将军和白将军早来了，为何却不唤姑娘陪酒？","tone":"调侃","chapter":202,"line_start":178,"line_end":180},{"speaker":"char_yang_duan_he","speaker_name":"杨端和","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"项大人上来前，酒楼内人人均在谈论大人明天一战的胜负，有人甚至吵得面红耳赤，我们听得入神，其他的事都忘了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":202,"line_start":182,"line_end":183},{"speaker":"char_bai_chong","speaker_name":"白充","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"当有人传来项大人已抵迎客厅的消息，厅内便哄动起来，有人说项大人必是稳操胜券，又有人说项大人不知……嘿不知……唉！都是不说了，总之现在没有人敢再说半句话。","tone":"无奈","chapter":202,"line_start":186,"line_end":188},{"speaker":"char_teng_yi","speaker_name":"滕翼","listener":"char_bai_chong","text":"是否不知自爱呢？","tone":"调侃","chapter":202,"line_start":190,"line_end":190},{"speaker":"char_xiao_pan","speaker_name":"小盘","listener":null,"text":"各位可随便召姑娘陪酒，不要因我而扫兴。","tone":"陈述","chapter":202,"line_start":208,"line_end":209},{"speaker":"char_wu_fu","speaker_name":"伍孚","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"杨豫姑娘唱毕一曲，立即过来相伴，她听到项大人来，其他客人都忘记了。","tone":"陈述","chapter":202,"line_start":216,"line_end":218},{"speaker":"char_xiang_shao_long","speaker_name":"项少龙","listener":"char_wu_fu","text":"今晚主客是远道而来的秦公子，杨豫是来陪他，而非陪我。","tone":"陈述","chapter":202,"line_start":220,"line_end":221},{"speaker":"char_wu_fu","speaker_name":"伍孚","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"大人放心，小人已分别通知美美、小蕾和燕燕，她们可以分身之时，立即来见秦公子，任公子罚酒罚唱。","tone":"陈述","chapter":202,"line_start":224,"line_end":225},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"嫪毐党羽","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"官当得大确是不同凡响，无论多红的姑娘都要委屈相从。","tone":"嘲讽","chapter":202,"line_start":230,"line_end":231},{"speaker":"char_li_si","speaker_name":"李斯","listener":null,"text":"在下只是如实告诉他们，储君下了严令，在决战前谁若斗胆干扰项大人，立斩无赦，故特别派出御卫贴身守护，负责执行命令。","tone":"淡然","chapter":202,"line_start":252,"line_end":254},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"王龁","listener":"char_xiang_shao_long","text":"本来还不相信，原来真是少龙来了，我们两个老家伙没有白走一趟。","tone":"大笑","chapter":202,"line_start":260,"line_end":261},{"speaker":null,"speaker_name":"王龁或王陵","listener":null,"text":"储君！","tone":"惊讶","chapter":202,"line_start":267,"line_end":267}],"new_entities":{"characters":[{"id":"char_chun_hua","name":"春花","alias":[],"identity":"醉风楼鸨婆","faction":null,"role":"npc","archetype":"healer","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"醉风楼鸨婆，管理姑娘们的中年妇人","personality":{"traits":["圆滑","善于逢迎","勤快","识时务","灵活"],"speech_style":"殷勤热情","temperament":"圆滑"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[202],"source_refs":[{"chapter":202,"line_start":82,"line_end":82,"text":"对正在旁相迎献媚的鸨婆春花爱理不理的"}]},{"id":"char_han_jie","name":"韩竭","alias":[],"identity":"嫪毐手下","faction":"faction_lao_ai_dang","role":"npc","archetype":"warrior","rank":"略有小成","one_line":"嫪毐手下，英伟轩昂的武士","personality":{"traits":["英伟","轩昂","忠诚","傲慢","好斗"],"speech_style":"傲慢","temperament":"刚烈"},"relationships":[{"target":"char_lao_ai","type":"主仆","intensity":70,"bond_level":3,"dynamic":"效忠嫪毐"}],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[202],"source_refs":[{"chapter":202,"line_start":200,"line_end":200,"text":"除英伟轩昂的韩竭外"}]},{"id":"char_lao_ai","name":"嫪毐","alias":[],"identity":"秦国权臣","faction":"faction_lao_ai_dang","role":"villain","archetype":"scholar","rank":"平平无奇","one_line":"秦国权臣，朱姬宠幸之人，党羽气焰嚣张","personality":{"traits":["野心勃勃","狡猾","嚣张","善于钻营","贪婪"],"speech_style":"阴险","temperament":"阴险"},"relationships":[],"known_skills":[],"related_skills":[],"rag_refs":[202],"source_refs":[{"chapter":202,"line_start":116,"line_end":116,"text":"只不知是否出自嫪毐意思"}]},{"id":"char_lao_si","name":"嫪肆","alias":[],"identity":"嫪毐手下","faction":"faction_lao_ai_dang","role":"npc","archetype":"assassin","rank":"平平无奇","